StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetOso369EvalChecklistDatesInfo]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@TrainingFileID uniqueidentifier
AS
BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT CompletedDate, SentToDistrictDate FROM USMC.Mul.MonthEvalua.on me, USMC.TrainingFile t
WHERE t.ID=@TrainingFileID AND me.TrainingFileID=t.ID
END
